stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> NoCode: Initial state

    NoCode --> Validating: applyPromoCode(code)
    Validating --> Applied: Code valid + subtotal qualifies
    Validating --> Error: Code invalid or subtotal too low

    Applied --> NoCode: removePromoCode()
    Error --> Validating: applyPromoCode(newCode)
    Error --> NoCode: Clear error

    state Applied {
        [*] --> DiscountActive
        DiscountActive: discount computed from code
        DiscountActive: total = subtotal - discount + shipping
    }

    state Error {
        [*] --> ShowError
        ShowError: promoError message displayed
    }